      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>In response to a petition (ʿarzdasht) from
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, <persName ref="#mutamadLalMuhammad">Mutamad Lal Muhammad</persName>
                is instructed not to threaten to attack the villagers in the districts (parganas) held in
              revenue assignment (jagir) by
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>.</p>
         </abstract>
