   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1663_dai_lns235ms_c1_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                     <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خان</persName>
                      مرید حضرت محمد
                     <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">اورنگ زیب</persName>
                      بادشاہ غازی</mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#mutamadLalMuhammad">معتمد لعل محمد</persName>
                بعنایت امیدوار بودہ بداند که دراینولا از عرضه داشت
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
                چودری پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دھار</placeName>
                بعرض رسید که او بر دھات پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#jamli">جاملی</placeName>
                رفته برعایا انجا
               <lb/>می گوید که بر دھات مذکور تاخت خواھم نمود و اینمعنی باعث بیدلی رعایا می گردد
               <lb/>لہذا نگاشته می آید کہ این معنی لغایت نا پسندیدہ نمود می باید که از پرگنات
               <lb/>جاگیر سرکار هیچ کار نداشته باشد و اگر مطلبی رو دھد حقیقت را عرضه داشت نماید که
               <lb/> ھر چه باید کرد بعمل خواھد آمد و اگر احیانًا ازین قسم افعال باز بخواھد آمد
               نتیجه نیک نخواھد یافت
               <lb/>درین باب نھایت تاکید دانسته از نوشته تخلف نورزد تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus">غرہ ذی حجہ سنہ
                  <num>٥</num>
               </date>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
                حسب المسطور عمل نماید
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1663_dai_lns235ms_c1_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p>
               <unclear>پروانہ</unclear>
                بنام
               <persName ref="#mutamadLalMuhammad">لعل محمد</persName>
                جیو</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>, disciple of Lord Muhammad
               <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Aurangzeb</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">Badshah</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_ghazi">Ghazi</ref>
         </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#mutamadLalMuhammad">Mutamad Lal Muhammad</persName>, having hoped for kindness, know that recently through the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">‘arzdasht</ref>
               <lb/>of
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, it has been represented that he [i.e. <persName ref="#mutamadLalMuhammad">Lal Muhammad</persName>] had gone to the villages of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#jamli">Jamli</placeName>
                and said to the peasants there
               <lb/>that he would invade the said <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>. And this has been the cause of the
               despair of the peasants there.
               <lb/>Therefore it is written that this event is extremely displeasing. It
               is necessary that he
               <lb/>have nothing to do with the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">parganas</ref> of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jagir">jagir</ref> of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">Sarkar</ref> [i.e. <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish
                  Khan</persName>]. And if any matters come forth, the facts should be put forward in an <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">‘arzdasht</ref> 
               <lb/>so that whatever needs to be done, can be done. And if he ever does
                this type of action again, the consequences will not be good.
               <lb/>Knowing this matter to be confirmed, do not neglect what is written.
               Written on the
               <date calendar="#julus">1st of Zi al-hijjah, [regnal] year 5</date>.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p>It must be done as written.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
            <p><unclear><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref></unclear> in the name of
               <persName ref="#mutamadLalMuhammad">Lal Muhammad</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
